title: Custom Model Home In Downtown Campbell, Luxurious Master Suite
posting_body: ['Custom Model Home In Downtown Campbell, Luxurious Master Suite, Gourmet Kitchen, A/C!', 'Property Address', '50 Waterford Court | Campbell, CA 95008', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'Presidential Real Estate, Inc', 'Description', '50 Waterford Court, Campbell, CA  95008  (Harrison/Civic Center)  Stunning Ainsley Square home featuring many fine finishes in this custom beauty!', 'Elegant hardwood floors, high ceilings and crown moldings, an abundance of windows and natural lighting.', ' Spacious master suite with gas fireplace, vaulted ceilings, walk-in closet, and luxurious master bath.', 'Kitchen features granite counters, obscured glass cabinet doors, & breakfast bar.', 'Small patio area with next to complex park.', 'Close to historic downtown campbell with restaurants, shopping, library, and light rail.', ' No pets except for service animals.', ' One year lease required.', 'Cal BRE# 01512831', 'Amenities', 'Model Tri-Story Home', 'Bonus Office/Den', 'Custom Hardwood Floors', 'Central Air Conditioning', 'Gourmet Kitchen with Breakfast Bar', 'Master Suite with Fireplace', 'Wood Stained Shutters', 'Lots of Natural Sunlight', 'Well Manicured Complex', 'Inside Downtown Campbell', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 2BD/3.0BA', 'Square Feet: 1,633', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $4,850.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $25.00', 'Security Deposit: $4,500.00']
